{
  "stem": "19596.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 340.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the door was open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the first one to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put ramps on the-- on the trucks, or near the trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was the first one to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was trying to push and push and shove and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, well, we saw-- as a matter of fact, it was nighttime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Trains almost most of the time arrived at nighttime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we saw dobermans and shepherds and SS and screaming and shouting, full of the whole-- ramp was full.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they told us, raus, raus, raus, and we went out and we stood there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And on the other trains, they were unloading the luggage, as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We noticed that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to ride up, and the women with the children, we are now separate, and the man separate, and so on and so on and so on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the whole ramp was full because the train was about, what?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were about 12 wagons or 15 wagons there, and each wagon took about 50 people or more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even more wagons.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we saw guys in stripes, and I couldn't work out what that they were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were helping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were helping people to get out and-- and I was talking to them, and--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was talking to them first in German, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then I heard they were [INAUDIBLE] and things like that, you know?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some, I heard them talk in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, you know, I couldn't speak Yiddish very well, because I never learned Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I only learned Yiddish in the camp itself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never spoke Yiddish before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They spoke back to me to be careful, and this and this, and they were trying to tell peoples a few things, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
